      <tr><td colspan=1  style='font-size: 9.5px;'>18 threads, <a href=item.html?item=6896&start=0>1</a>  page(s) long</td><td  style='font-size: 9.5px;' align=right>&nbsp;</td></tr></table></form><ul><table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=100459886481324></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f100459886481324><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=6896&mid=100459886481324>Illusions, illusions....</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=6896&mid=100459886481324#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=107969><span id= >Harmonic</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>13 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Nov 1st 2:14 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Iksar hide mask(bard/rogue)-iksar<br>Guise of the deciever(all)-dark elf<br>Mask of deception(bard/rogue)-dark elf<br>Mask of the coercer(bard/rogue)-high elf<br>Mask of obtenebration(bard/rogue)-erudite<br>Flayed barbarian mask(bard/rogue)-barbarian<br>Mask of the tinkerers(bard/rogue)-gnome<br>Ball of everliving golem(all)-earth elemental<br>Amulet of necropotence(all*)-skeleton<br>Neriad Shawl(bard/enc)-water elemental<br>Lute of the howler(bard)-werewolf<br>Dessicated halfling mask(bard/rogue/enc)-halfling<br><br>These are all the illusions I know of, the names I believe to be correct but could be slightly off.<br>All the classes can use and cast the illusion.<br>Aside from given racial abilities (infrasion/ultravision/factions/etc) the following illusions also include unique bonuses.<br><br>Werewolf grants you upto 30str, 100atk rating(not including str bonus) 40% spell haste, has unique faction adjustments including a bonus with chaotic-neutral creatures such as lions and tigers and bears (oh my) and even some undead. Although you will be KoS in almost all cities.<br><br>Earth elemental grants you a decent strength bonus.<br><br>Water elemental grants permanent enduring breath.<br><br>Skeleton has a quite useful (especially for PvP) bonus of immunity to blind, snares, and roots.<br><br>Iksar hide mask-Trakanon's Teeth<br>Guise of the deciever-Lower guk(no longer drops**)<br>Mask of deception-Lower guk<br>Mask of the coercer-Quest relating to rogue epic<br>Mask of obtenebration-Charasis<br>Flayed barbarian mask-Kael<br>Mask of the tinkerers-Sleeper's Tomb<br>Ball of everliving golem-Cazic Thule<br>Amulet of necropotence-Plane of Fear<br>Neriad Shawl-Siren's Grotto<br>Lute of the howler-Velketor's Lab.<br>Dessicated halfling mask-Chardok<br><br>*Amulet of necropotence can't be worn except by mag/nec/enc/wiz but can be used from the inventory by any class.<br><br>**Guise of the deciever was replaced by Mask of deception due to imbalance of game due to all class/races being able to be dark elves, it also didn't follow good roleplay..... gotta love those dark elf monks, rangers, paladins and many others. =)<br> <br>This is a pretty thorough listing of illusions, not the greatest detail but I hope it helps. I probably wont reply back to post, but feel free to leave corrections.<br>&nbsp;<br>"A stranger is a friend you just haven't met yet"<br>60th Virtuoso of Povar</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
