	   <tr><td colspan=2>OK, now, i know this sounds stupid but hear me out.<br>We had a chanter, a rogue, a bard, 2 tanks, and a cleric, now, we all agreed the chanter, bard, rogue should roll for it. So they did, the rogue won. The strange thing is, he's already a halfling, and the other members were very upset. This should go to who WINS the roll no matter what. the rogue is kos in his home city, and now, because of the mask, he is NOT! And besides, us halflings get bored with our look (as with all classes) instead of being the blonde one, now i can be the brown cute one!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
